2 3 4 2.2 ipsum
3 5 6 3.3 dolor
4 7 8 4.4 sit
NULL 9 10 5.5 amet
5 NULL 12 6.6 ,
6 11 NULL 7.7 consectetur
7 13 14 NULL adipiscing
8 15 16 8.8 NULL

